TITLE: Retrieval augmented scientific claim verification
AUTHORS: Liu; Chen; Biomedical NLP team
YEAR: 2024
TYPE: pubmed
VENUE: JAMIA Open
EVIDENCE: large_empirical
CITATIONS: 26
REPLICATION: 7200
RELEVANCE: 9200
CLAIM: Scientific claim verification can retrieve relevant trial abstracts and classify support, refute, or neutral evidence.
METHOD: PICO-based claim verification with retrieved PubMed abstracts.
LIMITATION: Biomedical claim verification does not directly prove general-purpose theory revision for all domains.
